tags: thanks for coming to my ted talk
summary:
Dan and Phil
I've been watching Dan and Phil for about 4 years now. They make me laugh. They make me smile. So I was pretty sad...
body:
Dan and Phil

I’ve been watching Dan and Phil for about 4 years now. They make me laugh. They make me smile. So I was pretty sad when I realised they wouldn’t be uploading a lot after Interactive Introverts. Don’t get me wrong, I loved the mukbang video, and everything after that. I understand that the break was for the best for them, and they deserve it. Then Phil started posting again, and I was back to loving their videos. (Also- loved their merch, I mean it doesn’t really have anything to do with this topic, but I just wanted to say [anyhow]) even though Phil was really only making videos. But anyways, I’ve been very thankful it’s summer break, because I have binged watched most of their videos, and yeah, my point is…. I am so happy they’re (hopefully/somewhat) coming back!

As always, thank you for coming to my Ted Talk, and here’s a little aesthetic thing I made
